<h2>The legal bit</h2>
<p>This offer allows Bupa members to claim 25% off all flower bouquets at appleyardflowers.com. The discount code can be used multiple times within the promotional period. The discount applies to all flower bouquets but excludes all other products such as hampers etc. Delivery not included. This offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other promotional offers or discounts. The discount is non-exchangeable, non-transferable and no cash alternative is offered.   </p>
<p>To redeem this offer customers must enter their promotional code at the checkout of appleyardflowers.com.     </p>
<p>The offer excludes delivery to the following postcodes :- AB, DD6 - DD11, EH35 - EH36, FK14, FK17 - FK21, GY, HS, IM, IV, JE, KA27 - KA28, KW, KY9 - KY16, PA20 - PA80, PH6 - PH99, TR21 - TR25, ZE.   </p>
<p>Appleyard reserves the right to hold, void, cancel, suspend, or amend the offer where it becomes necessary to do so. By accepting this offer, you are deemed to have accepted and agreed to be bound by these terms and conditions. This promotion will be governed by English law and subject to the jurisdiction of the English courts.</p>
